<br>
The next item that helped a whole lot was the R. Click Pants for B3. Saves a spell slot (I put COH in its place)<br>
<br>
I use the Decoy Pet with the 40 point built-in DS for exp camps.<br>
<br>
Our new Pet heal spells help a lot and the new mana/health regen. Phatasmal Armour upgrade spell is great(No more Cats Eye Agates)!<br>
<br>
I have played a 57 Warrior a 43 Monk a 60 ENC and a 36 Ranger 54 Wiz. and I keep coming back to my 58 Mage. I don't have any class envy. Having said that, each class has strengths that really add to a group or a guild. The only class that seems overlooked by Verant would be SK? They could really use a good class ability that guilds want?<br>
